<p>This week John and Dave turn it over to you, the listeners, to share all the tips, thoughts, follow-ups and responses you&#8217;ve had to recent shows. There were so many good tidbits in the mailbag over the past week or so that it made sense to devote a whole show to sharing all this juicy info. Download today, kick back, and increase your Mac knowledge with your two favorite geeks.</p>
